  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CAFOD supporters have donated to the Pope Francis Ukraine Appeal. This project will see the funds raised donated to the Pope&apos;s Initiative in Ukraine, an initiative where Caritas Internationalis has an advisory role on the how the funds are managed.

06/06/2017: The most urgent problem is now the lack of water in Lisichansk, Lugansk region. In this regard, we want to send your money to provide water to children&apos;s hospitals (about 500 children) in Lisichansk. We will provide this project through the Charity Organization &apos;Caritas Severodonetsk&apos;.</narrative>
